</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Top Level Domain</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the top level domain (TLD) from the drop-down list, e.g. <strong>co.uk</strong> or <strong>com</strong>.
You will see information about how much this domain will cost per month.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Confirm purchase</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Toggle the button (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-toggle-on  "></i></span>) to purchase the domain for the price shown.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Main domain</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">If you are creating a new subdomain for an existing main domain, then select the main domain from this list here.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Authcode</strong></p></td>
